+ tell [me] more about castling
- Castling can not be played when\n
^- The king is in check ie, under enemy attack
^- Either the King or Rook involved has previously moved
^- Pieces (eiter side) are between the king and the Rook
^- Squares passed over or landed on by the King are under enemy attack

