+what is (checkmate|mate)?
-Checkmate (often shortened to mate) is a game position in chess and
^other chess-like games in which a player's king is in check
^(threatened with capture ) and there is no way to avoid the threat.
^If a player is not in check but has no legal move, then it is stalemate,
^and the game immediately ends in a draw.


